titles.title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make technical corrections in the enrollment of H.R. 2918.

action.text: Pursuant to the provisions of H. Res. 772, H. Con. Res. 191 is considered passed House.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 9/30/2009--Passed Senate without amendment. Directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make technical corrections in the enrollment of H.R. 2918 (FY2010 legislative branch appropriations and continuing resolution).
